    "body": "### Problem\n\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/89f4dd37-7ab0-4b9e-84de-d2ad898e5c5a\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nnvim --clean -u init.lua foo.cc\n:lua vim.diagnostic.open_float()\n:Ex\n\n\n```lua init.lua\n-- init.lua\nvim.lsp.config['clangd'] = { cmd = { 'clangd' } }\nvim.lsp.enable('clangd')\n```\n\n```cpp foo.cc\n// foo.cc\n.\n```\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nNormal\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\n0.11.1\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nnone\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nmacOS 15.4.1\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\niTerm2 3.5.13\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nxterm-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nGithub Release Page",
